room_title: Escape room "Embalming Room Zombie Escape" by Mystere Escape Rooms in New Orleans
review: We did the zombie one and had to go back next day to do the serial killer. It was so much fun! We are now hooked on escape rooms. Our host was funny and kind.

room_title: Escape room "Embalming Room Zombie Escape" by Mystere Escape Rooms in New Orleans
review: My friends and I loved the Zombie room. The effects and decorations were amazing. We were a bit worried at first that it would be too scary, but it was exciting and we laughted so hard! The guy playing the zombie never stepped out of character!

room_title: Escape room "Embalming Room Zombie Escape" by Mystere Escape Rooms in New Orleans
review: This was a blast! My boyfriend and I went in the zombie's lair with only 2 other people. We finished with less than 10 seconds left. Can't wait to try another!

room_title: Escape room "Embalming Room Zombie Escape" by Mystere Escape Rooms in New Orleans
review: The experience is one to not miss ...I did it and I recommend you do too!!
